<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="worry-n">worry <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'wʌri/    美 /'wɜːri/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-anxiety">1.★ <strong>焦虑；担忧；烦恼 (anxiety)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She lost weight because of all the <strong>worry about</strong> her son’s illness.
她因为担心儿子的病情而消瘦了。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>令人担忧的事；让人发愁的事</strong></h4>
<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>worrying /'wʌriɪŋ/ adj   </p></div>